00:43:06.470 --> 00:43:12.210
On March 15 of that year Pedro
Menendez de Aviles signed a private

00:43:12.210 --> 00:43:17.570 position:56%
contract or [inaudible] with Spain's
King Philip II outlining the terms

00:43:17.570 --> 00:43:20.300
of a new conquest expedition
to Florida.

00:43:20.300 --> 00:43:24.700
An experienced mariner,
merchant and military commander,

00:43:24.700 --> 00:43:28.230
Menendez quickly began to recruit
colonists for his new venture.

00:43:28.230 --> 00:43:30.910
While many of them came
from Northern Spain,

00:43:30.910 --> 00:43:34.410
Menendez's forces included
men and women from other parts

00:43:34.410 --> 00:43:39.030
