00:47:26.520 --> 00:47:28.150
We're still playing with the name.

00:47:28.150 --> 00:47:32.940
And the hope is that 5 years
from now, 10 years from now,

00:47:32.940 --> 00:47:38.760
15 years from now we won't
have national history textbooks

00:47:38.760 --> 00:47:44.710
that begin the whole story of
colonization of the Americas

00:47:44.710 --> 00:47:46.150
and begin with Jamestown.

00:47:46.150 --> 00:47:49.710
But instead cover this more
than one century period

00:47:49.710 --> 00:47:53.650
that has been largely overlooked
in the national narrative.

00:47:53.650 --> 00:47:56.900
