00:50:53.720 --> 00:50:57.210
We'd love to do a section on
Spain and the American Revolution

00:50:57.210 --> 00:51:01.860
in Florida where there
were English colonies,

00:51:01.860 --> 00:51:04.030
East Florida and West Florida.

00:51:04.030 --> 00:51:11.260
So there this 13 colony
business is in fact not accurate.

00:51:11.260 --> 00:51:15.020
And a lot of loyalists of course
flee to East and West Florida.

00:51:15.020 --> 00:51:17.100
So we'd like to have
