00:56:18.740 --> 00:56:22.410
of the expedition came from.

00:56:22.410 --> 00:56:26.640
And I get a sense or a
hint that's an indication

00:56:26.640 --> 00:56:31.500
of Spain's global position because
it seems to, a lot of it seems

00:56:31.500 --> 00:56:33.440
to coincide with the
Holy Roman Emperor.

00:56:33.440 --> 00:56:34.740
&gt;&gt; J. Michael Francis: Yes.

00:56:34.740 --> 00:56:36.040
&gt;&gt; And I, the empire.

00:56:36.040 --> 00:56:38.240
And I don't remember how
many Spanish kings were

00:56:38.240 --> 00:56:40.240
in effect also Holy Roman Emperors.

00:56:40.240 --> 00:56:42.230
J. Michael Francis: Well in
this period it's just one.

00:56:42.230 --> 00:56:44.570
It's just Carlos Jesus.

00:56:44.570 --> 00:56:47.910
Charles I and then Charles
